OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Alicia Curry
OL,8,FIn a dramatic escalation of his
OL,9,F"reciprocal" trade strategy, US
OL,10,FPresident Donald Trump's sweeping
OL,11,Ftariffs on over 60 countries have now
