OL,3,CWhat are the US government long bonds
OL,4,Cand what can they forecast?
OL,6,FWhen confidence is low, bond prices
OL,7,Frise and yields fall as there is more
OL,8,Fdemand for this safe investment. Put
OL,9,Fsimply, falling yields indicate
OL,10,Fcaution in the markets.
OL,12,FHowever, in the current economic
OL,13,Fclimate, where Trump's new tariffs
OL,14,Fhave created a market of uncertainty,
OL,15,Finvestors are selling off existing
OL,16,Fbonds as opposed to holding onto this
OL,17,Ftraditionally safe asset.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
