OL,3,CWhat are the US government long bonds
OL,4,Cand what can they forecast?
OL,6,FInstability elsewhere in the economy
OL,7,Fis likely causing this. Investors may
OL,8,Fbe covering their losses elsewhere,
OL,9,Ffor example in tumbling stock prices,
OL,10,For for fear of the future economic
OL,11,Flandscape.
OL,13,FIt could also be a marker that US
OL,14,FTreasuries are losing their safe haven
OL,15,Fstatus.
OL,17,FAdditionally, China, which is said to
OL,18,Fhold $760 billion of US debt might be
OL,19,Fselling their bonds in order to
OL,20,Finflict more pain on the US government
OL,21,Fas part of the trade war.
