OL,6,FWhat is happening to US Treasuries?
OL,8,FThe yield - or interest rate - on the
OL,9,Fbenchmark 10-year US Treasury bond
OL,10,Frose by 0.16 percentage points on
OL,11,FWednesday to 4.42%, its highest since
OL,12,Flate February.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the 30-year Treasury bond
OL,15,Fjumped above 5% to its highest since
OL,16,Flate 2023.
OL,18,F"This is a fire sale of Treasuries,"
OL,19,FCalvin Yeoh, Blue Edge Advisors
OL,20,FPortfolio Manager, told Bloomberg.
