OL,6,FHigher borrowing rates mean higher
OL,7,Finterest rates which lead to higher
OL,8,Fmortgage and loan payments, and
OL,9,Freduced spending on public services.
OL,11,FTrump's tariff fallout has therefore
OL,12,Fheightened pressure on central banks
OL,13,Fand policymakers to act swiftly to
OL,14,Fprotect economies.
